    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When decorating the Zend_Captcha Form element, I use this:
        $this-&gt;captcha-&gt;setDecorators(
            array( 'Captcha',
                   'Description',
                   'Errors',
                   array(array('data'=&gt;'HtmlTag'), array('tag' =&gt; 'td')),
                   array('Label', array('tag' =&gt; 'td')),
                   array(array('row'=&gt;'HtmlTag'),array('tag'=&gt;'tr'))
        ));</p>

<p>The problem: the first TD HtmlTag element gets replaced by the last TR HtmlTag (after rendering). I have checked this, by removing the last decorator (the TR HtmlTag)</p>

